Remake: Lulu (FFX)
Weapon type: Unique
Crystal Color: Black
Spheres: A D D

Skill 1: Blizzard
 1-hit Ice Magic BRV+HP attack.
 Grants 1 stack of special effect [Doll Master] to self. (max 3)
 When [Doll Master] stacks are at 2, becomes Blizzara.
 When [Doll Master] stacks are at 3, becomes Blizzaga.
Skill 1 alt: Blizzara
 2-hit Ice Magic BRV+HP Attack.
 Grants 1 stack of special effect [Doll Master] to self. (max 3)
Skill 1 alt: Blizzaga
 3-hit Ice magic BRV+HP attack.
 Uses: 7
15cp: Mana Mog
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
c.55: Blizzard Extend
 +Adds 3 uses
 +Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+ while [Doll Master] is active
Blizzard:
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Becomes a 4-hit AoE Ice Magic BRV+HP attack
 +HP damage is distributed evenly
Blizzara:
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Becomes a 5-hit AoE Ice Magic BRV+HP attack
 +HP damage is distributed evenly
Blizzaga:
 +Tremendously increases BRV potency
 +Becomes a 6-hit AoE Ice Magic BRV+HP attack
 +HP damage is distributed evenly

[Doll Master]: Self: ATK Up (30%/40%/50%) based on stack count
                     BRV Regen (40%/60%/80% iBRV) based on stack count
               Party: Ice Enchant (20%)
                      Max BRV Up (20%/30%/40%) based on stack count
BRV Atack+: 2-hit Ice Magic BRV attack
            Raises party's BRV based on individual Max BRV

Skill 2: Heavenly Strike
 2-hit Ice Magic BRV attack.
 Delays target by 2 turns.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Ice Moomba
 +Adds 1 use
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Grants Max BRV Up (40%) to party for 6 turns
c.60: Heavenly Strike Extend
 +Adds 1 use
 +Grants BRV to party based on (40% of) own Max BRV before BRV hits
 +Becomes a 5-hit Ice Magic BRV+HP attack
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Deals 50% splash HP damage to non-targets
 +Inflicts Ice Resistance Down on all enemies for 4 turns
 +Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+ while [Doll Master] is active
 
HP Attack+: 2-hit Ice Magic BRV+HP attack
            Grants BRV to allies (excl. self) based on (50% of) HP damage dealt
 
EX: Booster Cactuar
 +Equips EX ability Blizzaga Fury
3-hit AoE Ice Magic BRV+HP attack, triggered 3 times.
Triggers 1 additional 3-hit AoE Ice Magic BRV+HP attack for each stack of [Doll Master] on self. (Max 6 times)
Inflicts Ice Resistance Down on all targets after first HP attack.
Grants [Alluring Mage] to self for 6 turns.
 Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Blizzaga Fury by 20%
  -LB3: Increases party Weakness damage dealt by 20%
 EX+: Greatly increases BRV potency
      Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (50%) and Max BRV (50%)
  -LB2: At Quest start:
        Grants [Alluring Mage] to self for 6 turns
        Grants 1 stack of [Doll Master] to self
        Grants Max BRV Up (40%) to party for 6 turns
  -LB3: Tremendously increases BRV potency
        Increases own BRV by 10% of TOTAL HP damage dealt after each HP attack (excl. last)

[Alluring Mage]: ATK Up (60%), Max BRV Up (40%)
                 Ice Enchant (20%)

LD: Space Bandit
 +Equips LD ability Diamond Dust
